{"tid":1937692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人在外地，已經唔夠廁紙用，仲要俾flatmate打飛機用矖我啲廁紙","createTime":"2020-03-22T05:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T12:02:07.000Z","uid":256113,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd280cb30e439237851c23907e009676fca208c","tid":1937692,"uid":256113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"屌本身已經好辛苦先買到一排廁紙，條支那仔乜撚嘢都唔買，用我嘅都算，但你老味宜家係用完我買唔撚到啊，一日都我用矖一卷。小妹屙屎先用3至4格，大嘅忍到沖涼前屙，抹幾下，直接沖涼，慳慳埋埋唔係俾你用嚟打飛機架仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以用水啊！咁撚唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱啱新嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隔左2個鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又隔多2個鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出門口前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返到嚟，冇矖<br />\n<br />\n真係痴撚線，廁紙當飯食咩"},{"pid":"0d1e01a147de5f9d862e839e84962342aec854b2","tid":1937692,"uid":290895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:40:50.000Z","msg":"打柒佢"},{"pid":"e5deb4da767baac8c04eadae1378ceb68ae508ae","tid":1937692,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"屌柒佢"},{"pid":"7686175f10fdfd5301b3ad98e0247f3d4244235a","tid":1937692,"uid":167295,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"去廁所先拎卷紙巾入去"},{"pid":"f9b53d004f1e62d3f250afe2419978d804a2eecd","tid":1937692,"uid":256113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7686175f10fdfd5301b3ad98e0247f3d4244235a","tid":1937692,"uid":167295,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"去廁所先拎卷紙巾入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"屌我宜家已經打算係咁，但我驚佢唔抹屎整污糟我個浴缸<img src=\"/assets/